  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Ed Psych &amp; Couns (Psychology)              : Selected theories, models, and concepts relevant to planning and reflecting upon educational practice and improvement. Overview of development, learning, thinking, motivation, individual difference, etc. In relation to applications in classroom teaching and learning, the complementary role of counsellors and psychologists, educational computing and technology. The Youth Protection Act.          </p>

